original_title: Chikara Young Lions Cup III - Night 3: Grapes Of Wrath
overview: July 24th, 2005 :: Not even the third annual Young Lions Cup can interrupt the pattern of "grape" themed named for our Pittston events. A 4-Corner Elimination tag bout is featured, alongside a wild relevos atomicos match. Plus an unforgettable tournament finals.
title: Chikara Young Lions Cup III - Night 3: Grapes Of Wrath
